chat_messages.text:
The user wants to create a mockup artifact for the UI. They want to add:
- Play button
- Skip button
- Toggle for platform (LinkedIn, iMessage)

I should wait for them to provide the mockup, or they might want me to create it. Let me wait to see if they want me to make it or they're going to make it themselves. They said "let me get a mockup artifact" which suggests they might make it, but could also be asking me to make one.

Actually, reading it again - "let me get a mockup artifact" - this could mean either:
1. They'll make it themselves
2. They want me to make an artifact

Given the conversation flow and that they said "perfect yeah" and then started describing additions, I think they're asking me to create the artifact with their specifications.

I should create a simple HTML artifact showing the UI mockup with:
- Play button and skip button at the top
- Platform toggle (LinkedIn, iMessage)
- The chat interface we discussed
- Clean, simple designI'll create a mockup artifact with the play/skip buttons and platform toggle. One sec:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Voice Profile Chat System</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #2a2a2a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .header {
            background: #1f1f1f;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .control-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .btn {
            background: #3a3a3a;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #4a4a4a;
        }

        .btn-play {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-play:hover {
            background: #45a049;
        }

        .btn-skip {
            background: #ff9800;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-skip:hover {
            background: #e68900;
        }

        .toggle {
            background: #3a3a3a;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .toggle-btn {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            color: #888;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .toggle-btn.active {
            background: #2196F3;
            color: white;
        }

        select {
            background: #3a3a3a;
            border: 1px solid #4a4a4a;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .status {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
            margin-left: auto;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .chat-area {
            height: 400px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #252525;
        }

        .message {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .message-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .message-content {
            background: #3a3a3a;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 70%;
        }

        .message.user .message-content {
            background: #2196F3;
            margin-left: auto;
        }

        .message.bot .message-label {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .tag {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            background: #4a4a4a;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .input-area {
            padding: 16px 20px;
            background: #1f1f1f;
            border-top: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            flex: 1;
            background: #2a2a2a;
            border: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #2196F3;
        }

        .btn-send {
            background: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
        }

        .btn-send:hover {
            background: #1976D2;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: #1f1f1f;
            border-top: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="title">Voice Profile Chat System</div>
            <div class="controls">
                <div class="control-group">
                    <button class="btn btn-play">▶ Play</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-skip">⏭ Skip</button>
                </div>

                <div class="toggle">
                    <button class="toggle-btn active">LinkedIn</button>
                    <button class="toggle-btn">iMessage</button>
                </div>

                <select>
                    <option>Professional-Direct</option>
                    <option>Professional-Technical</option>
                    <option>Professional-Collaborative</option>
                    <option>Casual-Creative</option>
                    <option>Tactical-Actionable</option>
                    <option>Romantic</option>
                </select>

                <div class="toggle">
                    <button class="toggle-btn active">Llama</button>
                    <button class="toggle-btn">Claude</button>
                </div>

                <div class="status">
                    <span class="status-dot"></span>
                    <span>Connected</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-area">
            <div class="message bot">
                <div class="message-label">
                    <span>Bot:</span>
                    <span class="tag">Simple</span>
                    <span class="tag">Greeting</span>
                </div>
                <div class="message-content">
                    Hey - ready when you are.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="message user">
                <div class="message-label">You:</div>
                <div class="message-content">
                    Want to connect on a fabrication project?
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="message bot">
                <div class="message-label">
                    <span>Bot:</span>
                    <span class="tag">Complex</span>
                    <span class="tag">General</span>
                </div>
                <div class="message-content">
                    Yeah, send files.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="input-area">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Type your message...">
            <button class="btn btn-send">Send</button>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <span>Characters: 18/20</span>
            <span>Profile: Professional-Direct</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Toggle button functionality
        document.querySelectorAll('.toggle').forEach(toggle => {
            toggle.querySelectorAll('.toggle-btn').forEach(btn => {
                btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    toggle.querySelectorAll('.toggle-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
                    btn.classList.add('active');
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

This mockup shows the UI with:
- **Play/Skip buttons** at top left
- **Platform toggle** (LinkedIn/iMessage)
- **Voice profile selector** dropdown
- **Backend toggle** (Llama/Claude)
- **Chat area** with tagged messages showing classification
- **Input area** with character count
- **Status indicators**

Want me to adjust anything?
